longBusinessSummary: Septeni Holdings Co., Ltd., through its subsidiaries, engages in the digital marketing and media platform businesses in Japan and internationally. The company provides digital marketing support, digital performance advertising, software development support, digital transformation support, real estate internet marketing, web marketing support, and cloud-based CRM services. It also provides ad network and platform; web services planning and development; and internet advertising services. It also produces animation; sells cosmetics; and provides specialized services for dating and matchmaking, as well as communication design, content management, and business support services. In addition, the company operates GANMA!, an intellectual property platform that provides manga artists training and support; ViViViT, a recruitment platform for matching designers with jobs; gooddo, a social contribution platform; and TowaStela, a childcare platform. The company was formerly known as Septeni Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Septeni Holdings Co., Ltd. in October 2006. Septeni Holdings Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
